title: Third Month Crazy Time
description: It's the third month, which means Third Month Crazy Time Brackets are BACK. This week Katie and Ashley take on naming the best ever Sports Movie (8:32). There's also a Bachelor Update (45:30), a Very Cavallari (58:20) Update, and a Whiskey Cavalier Update (5:55).
